::Social Proof Principle::Which Cialdini principle was demonstrated by the hotel towel study showing that "Most guests in this room reuse their towels" increased reuse by 33%?{
~Reciprocity #Reciprocity involves giving first to create obligation. The hotel study showed people following others' behavior (Social Proof).
